PrecisAppointment of THE HONOURABLE IONA V. CAMPAGNOLO, of Courtney, British Columbia, MAUREEN O'NEIL, of Ottawa, Ontario and JEAN-PIERRE SAINTONGE, of Brossard, Quebec, as directors of the Board of Directors of the International Centre for Human Rights and Democratic Development to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
